					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I'm honestly impressed by how much personality you somehow managed to infuse into a single ball bearing that kinda does nothing but hop out of boxes and roll a bit, and the fact that this tiny, harmless little thing is classified as Keter works wonders to put the Foundation's objectives into perspective. +1 from me.</p> 
